:

1. *Juče* sam video njegovu porodicu u gradu. (Yesterday I saw his family in the city.)
2. *Juče* sam izašla iz škole u pet sati. (Yesterday I left school at five o'clock.)
3. *Juče* je bilo mnogo ljudi u parku. (Yesterday there were a lot of people in the park.)
4. Znam da si *juče* došla doktoru. (I know you came to the doctor yesterday.)
5. *Juče* su se vratili iz inostranstva. (They returned from abroad yesterday.)